t-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/A19DAE7BECA668E672BD12D930C85849.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"962\" height=\"589\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/34A655916C7CBBCF17097B18A7C05DBB.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"670\" height=\"633\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/6EF71221DCA7DBFD6880FBDBFDE6164F.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"424\" height=\"316\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/BEB28C90F565C2C90AA705845FCE8CE0.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"420\" height=\"435\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/46C804D1747E14473BDD3AE9BCA22656.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"647\" height=\"431\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">客户端还有很多细节功能，比如头像有三种显示模式、好友上线动画、聊天记录、聊天自动回复功能等，有兴趣的同学可以自己探索尝试一下吧，这里就不截图了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面介绍一下服务器代码和pc客户端代码的编译与运行环境：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">flamingo服务器端代码使用cmake + makefile编译，使用了纯C++11开发，运行于linux系统下（我的系统是CentOS7.0），为了支持C++11，你的gcc版本至少要大于4.7，我的版本是4.8.5。另外，使用了mysql数据库，我的数据库版本是5.7.17。我实际安装的是mysql的开源分支mariadb，安装方法如下：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">MariaDB数据库管理系统是MySQL的一个分支，主要由开源社区在维护，采用GPL授权许可。开发这个分支的原因之一是：甲骨文公司收购了MySQL后，有将MySQL闭源的潜在风险，因此社区采用分支的方式来避开这个风险。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">MariaDB的目的是完全兼容MySQL，包括API和命令行，使之能轻松成为MySQL的代替品。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">安装mariadb，大小59 M。</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 5px; margin: 5px 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\"><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow-x: auto; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[root@yl-web yl]<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">#</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\"> yum install mariadb-server mariadb mariadb-devel</span></pre></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">mariadb数据库的相关命令是：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">systemctl start mariadb &nbsp;#启动MariaDB</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">systemctl stop mariadb &nbsp;#停止MariaDB</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">systemctl restart mariadb &nbsp;#重启MariaDB</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">systemctl enable mariadb &nbsp;#设置开机启动</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">所以先启动数据库</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 5px; margin: 5px 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\"><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow-x: auto; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[root@yl-web yl]<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">#</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\"> systemctl start mariadb</span></pre></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">然后就可以正常使用mysql了</p><div class=\"cnblogs_code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 5px; margin: 5px 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\"><div class=\"cnblogs_code_toolbar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 5px 0px 0px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"cnblogs_code_copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><a title=\"复制代码\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 3px; border: none;\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/51E409B11AA51C150090697429A953ED.gif\" alt=\"复制代码\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in; padding: 0px; border: none;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a></span></div><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow-x: auto; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; white-space: pre-wrap;\">[root@yl-web yl]<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">#</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); line-height: 1.5;\"> mysql -u root -p</span>\n<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\">Enter password: \nWelcome to the MariaDB monitor.  Commands end with ; </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">or</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"> \\g.\nYour MariaDB connection id </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">is</span> 3<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\">\nServer version: </span>5.5.41-<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\">MariaDB MariaDB Server\n\nCopyright (c) </span>2000, 2014, Oracle, MariaDB Corporation Ab <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">and</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"> others.\n\nType </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">help;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span> <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">or</span> <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\\h</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span> <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">for</span> help. Type <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">\\c</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;\">'</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"> to clear the current input statement.\n\nMariaDB [(none)]</span>&gt;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"> show databases;\n</span>+--------------------+\n| Database           |\n+--------------------+\n| information_schema |\n| mysql              |\n| performance_schema |\n| test               |\n+--------------------+\n4 rows <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 1.5;\">in</span> set (0.00<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"> sec)\n\nMariaDB [(none)]</span>&gt; </pre><div class=\"cnblogs_code_toolbar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 5px 0px 0px; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"cnblogs_code_copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px; line-height: 1.5;\"><a title=\"复制代码\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 128, 0); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 1px 3px; border: none;\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/51E409B11AA51C150090697429A953ED.gif\" alt=\"复制代码\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in; padding: 0px; border: none;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a></span></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 20.88px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">安装mariadb后显示的也是&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">MariaDB [(none)]&gt;&nbsp;</span>，可能看起来有点不习惯。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">服务器代码不仅是一款即时通讯软件的服务器代码，同时也是一款通用的C++11服务器框架。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">服务器代码使用方法：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">编译方法：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 进入程序目录，输入cmake . (注意有一个点号，表示当前目录)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 没有错误，输入make</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.最终会产生两个可执行程序，mychatserver和myfilesever。编译完成</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">部署方法：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简单说明：mysql数据库的用户名为root，密码为空，请根据你自己的需要设置相应的用户名和密码（目前写死在程序中）。mychatserver是聊天服务器，myfileserver是文件服务器，文件服务器负责上传和下载聊天中发送的文件，myimgserver负责上传和下载聊天中的图片。三个服务相互独立，互不影响。聊天服务器监听端口是20000，文件服务器端口是20001，图片服务器端口号是20002，这三个端口供客户端连接，其中聊天端口和客户端是长连接，文件端口和图片可选择长连接或短连接。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第一次运行mychatserver时，如果能顺利连上mysql，mychatserver会自动检测是否存在名为myim的数据库，如果不存在则创建，并新建三张信息表，分别是用户信息表：t_user, 好友关系表t_user_relationship和聊天消息记录表t_chatmsg。第一次启动文件服务器时会创建filecache目录，这个目录用来存储聊天中的聊天图片和离线文件以及客户端升级包。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; white-space: pre;\"></span>为了方便查看代码，我用Visual Studio来管理代码，可使用VS打开myserver.sln查看和管理代码。（VS版本必须是VS2013或以上版本）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">客户端代码使用方法：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">编译：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.用VS2013打开程序目录下的：Flamingo.sln，你可以使用其他的VS版本，但是至少不低于VS2013，因为客户端代码也使用了大量C++11语法和库，VS2013及以上版本才能较好的支持C++11的语法。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 打开的解决方案包括三个项目：Flamingo是即时通讯主程序，CatchScreen是聊天中使用的截图工具，iUpdateAuto是升级功能中用到的解压工具。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 用VS2013编译整个解决方法即可，编译成功以后将在Bin目录下生成对应的程序。启动Flamingo.exe注册一个账号就可以开始使用flamingo了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">如果你暂时不想研究服务器代码，但又想使用客户端，你可以连接我的测试服务器，测试服务器地址是：</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">聊天服务器地址：120.55.94.78 端口号：20000</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">文件服务器地址：120.55.94.78 端口号：20001</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">图片服务器地址：120.55.94.78 端口号：20002<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"></span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; 